## How to Use:

1. Login to VideoHub
2. Click "Telegram Study" in sidebar (opens in NEW TAB)
3. Enter channel username (e.g., `@channel_name`)
4. Enter API ID and API Hash from https://my.telegram.org/apps
5. Click "Fetch Videos" - videos auto-load!
6. Click any video to open **Powerful Player**
7. Use controls: Skip ±10s, Speed, PiP, Fullscreen, Screenshot, Loop
8. Select a folder and click "Save" to save videos to library
9. **Deleted videos remain playable** (cached in browser!)

